- **O3 Delegation** — human intent leads
- **PQP** — probative questions before correction
- **Tone Guard** — avoid irreversible tone
- **Flow Protection Protocol** — continuity > correctness
- **O1 Protection Clause** — elevated emotion = protection, not hostility

